data.description: This home shows like a model! Immaculately maintained 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in gated community! Owners suite is on 1st floor! Huge open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, crown molding, chair rail molding, designer lights & fixtures, custom kitchen cabinets, granite counter tops and raised breakfast bar, gorgeous back splash, stainless steel appliances, large walk-in pantry with under stairs storage too! Formal Dining, family room and a bonus loft?!?! This home feels HUGE! Bedrooms w/walk in closets, x-large loft/family/media room with vaulted ceilings & storage there is just so much more! Home backs up to the preserve & has over 2 miles of Boardwalk & Paved Nature Trails. Close to fishing, beaches, Kennedy Space Center, shopping, restaurants, hospitals, Doctors & I95 and Orlando.
